overdue.
   The baby was delivered after a difficult pregnancy that forced
her mother, Lisa Dukakis, 33, to remain in bed for months and
abandon the presidential campaign that occupied the rest of the
family for most of 1988.
   The new father, John Dukakis, 30, the son of Mrs. Dukakis' first
