<HEAD>London Shares Down But Above Lows</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: will be led after closing</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Stock prices headed lower at midday Wednesday,
although they were off the morning's low point.
   The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-share index was off 8.6
points, or 0.4 percent, at 2,043.2 around 12:30 p.m. local time,
